name: Brian William Treece
description: People consider me kind, honest and reliable. I am not perfect, but I have a lot of good qualities such as sincerity, understanding and patience. I really love nature, long walks and just being in the forest or near the water. I enjoy going out and spending my spare time in a company of good friends. I also like cooking something special; I enjoy fine candle-light dinners. I like traveling and adventures. But my main passion is music… I know how music influence and changes the mood, that is why I prefer to start my day by turning on my radio or CD player and dancing while getting ready to go to work. I am sincere in my feelings, deeds and attitude to people. I cannot lie. I like and can listen to other people. I have a gentle character and cannot quarrel and call names. I am tolerant to other people weak points. All of us are different.
